title: Statistics released on experience of the public library service and experience of museums and science ...
text: ( Source : Northern Ireland Executive ) The Department of Culture , Arts and Leisure today released figures on experience of the public library service and experience of museums and science centres by adults in 2014/15. ~ Thursday, 22 October
